{"id": "issue-8a24c0", "title": "Add FTS5 full-text search to planner skill", "description": "Add FTS5 full-text search to planner tasks.\n\n**Current state:**\n- No FTS index on planner_queue table\n- Simple tag/project filtering only\n\n**Implementation:**\n- Create planner_queue_fts virtual table indexing issue_id, tags, project_id\n- Add triggers for automatic sync\n- Update search() method to use FTS5\n- Enables queries like: `planner search \"authentication backend\"`\n\n**Benefits:**\n- Fast search across queued tasks\n- Better task discovery\n- Consistent with issues FTS implementation\n\n**Reference:** issue-65b332", "status": "open", "priority": 2, "type": "feature", "assignee": null, "epic_id": null, "labels": ["enhancement", "fts", "search"], "created_at": "2025-11-16T00:44:39.739510", "updated_at": "2025-11-16T00:44:39.739510", "closed_at": null, "project_id": "default"}
